version_description: Fireside has some great tabs which already exist. But this version is easier to play for the arctic monkey lovers because a capo on the 5th fret works like magic. Godspeed.
An easier version for beginners(with capo), including the intro tab and the chords for the whole song.
Included the main riff at the beginning. Chorus and Bridge sounds like arpeggio picking. Enjoy~.
